<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <style>
        /* Style the entire section */
        section.sample-page {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        /* Style the heading */
        h1 {
            font-size: 54px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Style the paragraph text */
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Style the link */
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            /* Hover state for the link */
            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- ======= Header ======= -->


    <main id="main">



        <section class="sample-page">
            <div class="container">

                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

                <p>
                    Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website.
                </p>

                <h3>Information we collect</h3>

                <p>
                    We may collect information about you and your use of our service, your interactions with us and our advertising, as well as information regarding your computer or other devices used to access our service.
                </p>

                <h3>Use of information</h3>

                <p>
                    We use the information to provide, analyze, administer, enhance and personalize our services and marketing efforts, to process your registration, your orders and your payments, and to communicate with you on these and other topics.
                </p>

                <h3>Your choices</h3>

                <p>
                    If you do not wish to receive promotional emails, text messages, or other communications, you may opt out of receiving them at any time.
                </p>

                <p>
                    If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please <a href="/Home/ContactUs">contact us</a>.
                </p>
            </div>

        </section>


    </main><!-- End #main -->

</body>
</html>


